    <date day="27" month="August" year="2013"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>This draft describes a mechanism for adding generalized multi-
   protocol support to the Locator/ID Separation Protocol (LISP)
   [RFC6830].  Protocol identification is carried in the LISP header and
   is used to describe the encapsulated payload.</t>
    </abstract>
